# ovh_vps_available_images (Data Source)

Use this data source to retrieve the list of available images for an OVHcloud VPS.

## Example Usage

{{tffile "examples/data-sources/vps_available_images/example_1.tf"}}

## Argument Reference

* `service_name` - (Required) The service_name of your VPS.

## Attributes Reference

(See generated docs/data-sources/vps_available_images.md for the full attribute list.)

* `id` - The ID of the data source.
* `result` - The list of available image IDs for this VPS.
